<br>
I see a lot of monks soloing.  But in groups and dungeons a good monk is desirable for pulling and for damage output.<br>
<br>
Warriors are essential tanks in groups and definitely are more effective grouped, but I see a few LFG a lot because there are so many warriors.<br>
<br>
Rogues are fun because they are generally damage-dealers who don't necessarily have to pull though they can.  I see LFG tags on rogues though, possibly because some people would rather have other classes in group, and because rogues need groups with a taunting tank in order to be effective.<br>
<br>
